  "texts": [
    "To evaluate these poems, we need to consider each dimension to grasp the key elements and compare them effectively.",
    "The prompt is to reflect on the experience of remembering the dead and perceiving death in contrast to major disasters like the Titanic.",
    "This prompts us to focus on both human and naturalistic death, the impact of memory, and the honor and acceptance of grief.",
    "Both poems satisfy the prompt by offering reflections on the human condition related to death.",
    "They both focus on encounters with those who were absent in disasters and how death intrudes on life."
  ]
}